            long double new_zr = zr*zr-zi*zi+cr;
            long double new_zi = 2*zr*zi+ci;
            zr = new_zr; 
            zi = new_zi;
        }
        return 1;
    }

Also, using `cpowl` for simple squaring will result in inaccuracies that can be avoided by simplying using `z*z` in this case.

